    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>As a developer, I need to integrate the chatbot into the application so that it helps the user understand how it works and interpret the data it provides. It should also generate a PDF document with an executive and technical report and offer the option to send it to the user via email.</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
